<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Primeiro acesso</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: #e11d48;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #e11d48;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }

        .footer h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.75rem;
        }

        strong {
            color: #e11d48;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Nova conta</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Olá {{name}},</p>
            <p>Seus dados de acesso são:</p>
            <p><strong>Usuário:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Senha:</strong> {{password}}</p>
            <p>Para acessar o sistema, clique no botão abaixo:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <h1><span style="color: #e11d48">FA</span>Tracker</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>